values:
classNames(
    "progressive-disclosure-header",
    { "progressive-disclosure-header--open": isOpen,
        "progressive-disclosure-header--close_with_callout": !isOpen && showCallout,
        "progressive-disclosure-header--loading": state === ProgressiveDisclosureState.Loading,
        "progressive-disclosure-header--disabled": state === ProgressiveDisclosureState.Pending })

{
    base:
        integration.configurationStatus === IntegrationStatus.NotAvailableYet || shouldOpen
            ? undefined
            : "var(--hop-space-inset-md)",
    md: "var(--hop-space-inline-xs)"
}

{
    fontSize: "1.25rem",
    fontWeight: 410,
    lineHeight: 1.2,
    letterSpacing: "-0.05rem",
    fontFamily: "var(--hop-font-family-primary)",
    color: "var(--hop-neutral-text)",
    ...style
}

{
    background: "linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(135, 218, 178, 0.20) 7.8%, rgba(164, 202, 247, 0.50) 95.84%)",
    borderRadius: "4px",
    height: "40px",
    width: "40px",
    display: "flex",
    justifyContent: "center",
    alignItems: "center"
}

{
    width: "100%",
    height: "512px",
    position: "relative",
    paddingLeft: isDesktop ? "60px" : "30px",
    paddingTop: "30px",
    paddingBottom: isDesktop ? "60px" : "30px" }

{
    position: "absolute",
    height: "100px",
    width: "8px",
    left: 0,
    top: "50%",
    transform: "translateY(-50%)"
}

{
    position: "relative",
    width: "100%",
    height: "100%",
    display: "flex",
    alignItems: "flex-end",
    justifyContent: "space-between",
    paddingRight: "5%"
}

{
    display: "flex",
    justifyContent: "space-between",
    width: "100%",
    height: "100%",
    position: "relative",
    paddingLeft: "5%"
}

{
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    alignItems: "center",
    flex: 1,
    margin: "0 2%",
    justifyContent: "flex-end",
    position: "relative"
}

{
    position: "absolute",
    bottom: "0",
    left: "50%",
    transform: "translateX(-50%)",
    height: "8px",
    width: "100px"
}

{
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    alignItems: "stretch",
    border: "0.0625rem solid var(--hop-neutral-border-weak)",
    borderRadius: "0.5rem"
}
() => submitPrompt("How do I report a sick day?")
isLeft ? "Go to previous pages" : "Go to next pages"

{
    display: "flex",
    width: "15.25rem",
    padding: "inset-squish-md inset-md",
    justifyContent: "center",
    alignItems: "center"
}

(<IconButton size="sm"
    aria-label="send"
    onClick={onSubmit}
    backgroundColor={isButtonEnabled ? "var(--hop-orchid-bloom-600)" : undefined}
    borderRadius="circle"
>
    <ArrowUpIcon fill={isButtonEnabled ? "neutral-strong" : "neutral-weakest"} size="sm" />
</IconButton>)
(e, v) => onChange({ ...attribute, value: v ? parseInt(v) : null })
(event: SyntheticEvent, key: string[]) => { close(event); onFilterValueSelectionChange(new Map<string, string[]>([[filter.id, key]])); }
